---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="Property Auctions | Property App 2026" description="Auction-ready property inventory for land, houses, and flats.">
  <section class="auction-hero card">
    <div>
      <span class="pill">Auction inventory</span>
      <h1>Property auctions without burying the buyer in guesswork.</h1>
      <p>
        Use auctions for land, houses, and flats where timing, reserve expectations, and decision pressure matter.
        This is the structured route into auction-led inventory before a full live bidding engine is introduced.
      </p>
      <div class="hero-actions">
        <a class="button-dark" href="/listings/?intent=buy&saleMode=auction">Browse auction listings</a>
        <a class="button-secondary" href="/submit-listing/">Post auction inventory</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="auction-grid section-gap">
    <article class="card auction-card">
      <strong>For buyers</strong>
      <p>See the auction window, opening bid, reserve guidance, and terms before you commit to deeper due diligence.</p>
    </article>
    <article class="card auction-card">
      <strong>For owners</strong>
      <p>Use auction mode when timing and structured demand matter more than slow negotiated back-and-forth.</p>
    </article>
    <article class="card auction-card">
      <strong>For the marketplace</strong>
      <p>This adds a high-attention inventory route that most regional portals still treat weakly or not at all.</p>
    </article>
  </section>

  <style is:inline>
    .auction-hero,
    .auction-card {
      padding: 1.4rem;
    }

    .auction-hero h1 {
      margin: 0.75rem 0 0;
      font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3.5rem);
      line-height: 0.94;
      letter-spacing: -0.08em;
      max-width: 12ch;
    }

    .auction-hero p,
    .auction-card p {
      color: var(--muted);
      line-height: 1.72;
    }

    .hero-actions {
      display: flex;
      gap: 0.75rem;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      margin-top: 1rem;
    }

    .button-dark,
    .button-secondary {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      min-height: 2.9rem;
      border-radius: 999px;
      padding: 0.84rem 1rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      text-decoration: none;
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
    }

    .button-dark {
      background: var(--brand);
      color: var(--surface-canvas);
      border-color: var(--brand);
    }

    .button-secondary {
      background: var(--surface-elevated-strong);
      color: var(--text);
    }

    .auction-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr));
      gap: 1rem;
    }

    @media (max-width: 860px) {
      .auction-grid {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }
    }
  </style>
</Layout>
